  Signal Processing LSI for BS/CS Tuner PD6396A, 
PC2742. 
Isao Nakayama, Hiroshi Inose, Yumiko Goka, Senzi Kikuchi, 
Masayuki Takori, Takashi Kaneko, and Toshiyuki Kitamoto, pp 
174-179 
  NEC has developed the PD6396A and PC2742 as signal 
processing LSIs for communication and broadcasting satellites. 
The PD6396A is a single-chip LSI having a PCM demodulator, 
digital filter, D/A converter and function blocks for 
de-scrambler. The PC2742 is a single-chip LSI having a QPSK 
